{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty."}]}],"name":"url"},{"name":"headers","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This is useful for:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Regional compliance","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network monitoring"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Firewall restrictions"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"while preserving all headers and request body content.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"}}}